metadata.name: Breath of Light
metadata.description:
Digital, 30 x 140", 2019 

Awaken dear spirit
do you remember? 
Your eternal divine nature? 

It is time to face the facets
of this mystical mystery,
Play with the physical and metaphysical,
of dreams and reality. 

Between the formless of form,
your emotions and sensations,
there is a symphony of silence,
within the light of your soul.
